option.value:
from nonebot import on_startswith from nonebot.rule import to_me from nonebot.plugin import PluginMetadata from nonebot.matcher import Matcher from nonebot.adapters.onebot.v11 import Message, MessageEvent, MessageSegment
__plugin_meta__ = PluginMetadata( name="Beta Plugin", description="A plugin for testing new features.", usage="Send 'b' to trigger the beta feature.", )
beta_pa = on_startswith("b", rule=to_me(), priority=2, block=True)
@beta_pa.handle() async def rebirth_handler(matcher: Matcher, event: MessageEvent): await matcher.finish(Message([MessageSegment.text('啪！')]))
